data.description: **Seller has a $475k assumable FHA loan at 4.25%** Discover this thoughtfully renovated Willoughby Acres home, set on .24 acres with Southern exposure. The open floor plan and flexible spaces are perfect for hosting/entertaining. This split-bedroom design encompasses 3 beds, 2 baths, and 2115 sqft. The master bath features floor-to-ceiling polished marble, while the reconfigured walk-in closet boasts custom built-ins. Updates abound, from new fixtures, moldings, and quartz countertops to custom cabinetry and porcelain plank tiles throughout. Outside, a new paver driveway leads to a privately fenced backyard with a 320 sqft air-conditioned casita/cabana and an upgraded open lanai with ample room for a pool. The exterior was recently painted in August '23, complementing the new roof in 2015, with impact windows/doors/sliders, and is located in flood zone X, offering added peace of mind. Situated only 10 minutes away are Vanderbilt Beach, Delnor-Wiggins State Park, and the charming boutique shops and dining options of Mercato. Conveniently located just 5 minutes to I-75, this property features no rental restrictions and is positioned within one of Naples's top school districts.
